    public class AdidasCountryCodeSpinner<T extends android.os.Parcelable>
extends AdidasIndexableSpinner<T>
    Custom AdidasCountryCodeSpinner This widget behaves like a AdidasIndexableSpinner to display a long list (country list) In addition provides the filtering feature through the SearchView where the user input is fetched and the list is filtered through the FilterableAdapter.
